You didn’t mention if the tv was still valid or not. If the AprilTag overfills the image then it goes invalid.

You likely aren’t using MegaTag or MegaTag2 since you mentioned tx but those have limits, also. MegaTag2 cannot get as close to the tag (by about 2 inches or so) as MegaTag which can approach the tag all the way to filling the image.
